⇧ ⌘ '       => Maximize tool window
f12         => show terminal tool window
⌘ 9         => show version control tool window
⌘ 3         => show find tool window
^ ⌘ ⌥ =     => increase font size
^ ⌘ ⌥ -     => decrease font size
^ ⌘ ⌥ v     => split vertically
^ ⌘ ⌥ h     => split horizontally
⌥ ⇥         => go to next splitter
^ w ^ k     => change splitter orientation
⌘ ⌫         => delete line
⌥ ⌦         => delete to word end
⌥ ⌫         => delete to word start
^ ⌘ ⌥ d     => put editor in full screen (toggle distraction free mode)
⌘ ⌃ F       => toggle full screen
^ ⌘ ⌥ c     => compare with branch
